---
import BasicLayout from '../layouts/Basic.astro'
import LinkedIn from '../components/icons/LinkedIn'
import Github from '../components/icons/Github'
import Paperclip from '../components/icons/Paperclip'
---

<BasicLayout>
	<div>
		<h1 class="text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight">George Butler</h1>
		<h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight">Computer Graphics Engineer</h2>
		<p class="mt-3 max-w-xs leading-normal">I build immersive, unique, and accessible digital experiences.</p>
		<div class="flex flex-row gap-4 mt-3">
			<a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" class="inline-block">
				<Github size='1.5rem'/>
			</a>
			<a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" class="inline-block">
				<LinkedIn size='1.5rem'/>
			</a>
			<a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" class="inline-block">
				<Paperclip size='1.5rem'/>
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div>
		<p>Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Et cumque, id numquam repellat ullam magnam laboriosam. A tempora itaque ipsa voluptate eveniet corporis maxime fugiat quibusdam! Ratione inventore magni iste!</p>
	</div>
	<div>
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-2 items-center">
			<p class="max-w-xs leading-normal">Copyright &copy; 2024 George Butler.</p>
			<div class="flex flex-row gap-4">
				<a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" class="inline-block">
					<Github size='1rem'/>
				</a>
				<a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" class="inline-block">
					<LinkedIn size='1rem'/>
				</a>
				<a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" class="inline-block">
					<Paperclip size='1rem'/>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</BasicLayout>
